Text: In an effort to prevent the federal fund rate rising further the central bank added more money into the system on Thursday. So far this week $203 billion has been injected into the markets.
Cause: In an effort to prevent the federal fund rate rising further the central bank added more money into the system on Thursday.
Effect: So far this week $203 billion has been injected into the markets.
